Welcome back to the cooking class of the world popular chef – Sara – who has excellent cooking skills inherently. In Chicken Fajitas: Sara Cooking Class game, you as an online gamer will get a chance to learn how to prepare the best quality chicken fajitas in a friendly and cool environment. Your goal in this exciting free online cooking game for girls is to follow Sara instructions with an open mind to get your delicious dish prepared shortly. Sara is very helping in nature, so you will not face difficulty in learning from her. 

You need to go through each and every segment of the Sara cooking class to complete the task timely. When you play this cool flash girls game in your browser, it is common to try this dish at your home in real. You are sure to surprise your family and friends with the serving of an extremely scrumptious meal. Be careful since these chicken fajitas are very delicious but very spicy. It is easy to make them a little bit refreshing and mouthwatering with pickled peppers, chopped onions and tomato paste. 

This challenging free online cooking game features excellent gameplay, classic graphics and easy control for online gamers. You can rest assured of having the unlimited fun and excitement while exploring this most in-demand cooking game. So, what are waiting for? Test your cooking skills and time-management skills to get this mouth-watering dish prepared for your loved ones!
